<br>
It seems there is adequate interest to start up a weekly Vox raid. The goal - beyond just plain fun times - is to clear a backlog of white scale (Bard Epic) and Forst Torn Book (Pally Epic) needs that exist on Povar. This is to be an open raiding schedule, but signups will be taken before those not signed up, and regulars before newbs (those that support the project regularly should be supported) <br>
<br>
